  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Aim: To study the basic technical skills of colonoscopy using a MS Kinect for motion
      analysis. In order to develop a non-biased tool to monitor competence.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      To compare a group of novices to a group of experienced endoscopists performining
      colonoscopy.

      Analyzing the motion pattern of the performers using a Kinect. Use the contrasting group
      method to set standards.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
